name: Ambrose Wharton
description: I am a sincere, loving, kind, affectionate and dependable person. Forthright and honest, I value integrity – a sense of fairness. One has to be able to look in the mirror and be comfortable with the values and character they show to the world. I have an outgoing attitude, am positive-minded in nature and spontaneous towards new experiences. I like to laugh and have been described as having a good sense of humor
